Package edu.metrostate.ics372.thatgroup.clinicaltrial.catalog

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TrialCatalog
    The TrialCatalog interface is used to access the data of a specific trial.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClinicalStatement  
    ClinicalTrialCatalog
    The ClinicalTrialCatalog serves as the central database used to store all of the information for a trial.
    ClinicalTrialCatalogUtilIty
    The ClinicalTrialCatalogUtilIty is used to find the specific storage path for the trial catalog(s), get connections to the catalogs, and write and initialize new trial catalogs in the directory.
    ClinicalTrialDatabaseTest  
    TrialManager
    The TrialManager is responsible for returning a Singleton instance of a this class.
